00:28:48,640 --> 00:28:51,740
The core insight here is that different discourse communities

498
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:54,540
define semantic equivalents completely differently.

499
00:28:55,280 --> 00:28:59,620
What constitutes a brilliant, acceptable paraphrase to a literary fiction editor

