00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:59,280
The paper actually quantifies this difference using a formula for domain rigidity.

515
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:05,960
It's Rp equals the norm of omega over kappa max, Rp, omega p kappa max, Rp.

