00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:31,660
Literary text is an open field where you can wander in wide circles.

534
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:34,640
Legal text is a tightrope over an abyss.

535
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:44,220
And the true beauty of Proposition 8.4 in this paper is that the perturbation engine itself, the algorithmic machine doing the walking, never changes.

